    "Html": "Hi,<br>\r\nCreating and Binding at runtime or code behind is possible with DatGridColumn together with DatGridBoundColumn.<br>\r\nI would like to create and bind to a <span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515;font-family:'courier new'\">DataGridTemplateColumn </span>at runtime or code behind.<br>\r\nThe control I want to bind to is a DatePicker.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPlease help.<br>\r\nWorstCase<br>\r\n",
